- Launch the OpenShift UI
- Mine to Workloads-->Secrets
- Switch to the cp4a namespace
- Edit the cp4a namespace "letsencrypt-certs" secret


- Add a new key/value pair with the key name of "ca.crt"
- Cut the contents of the second cert in the "tls.crt", leaving just a single cert. 
- Paste the second cert into the value of the new "ca.crt" 
- Save the secret
